api_list.description:
Search for-sale properties.
**Parameters**: `zipcode, limit, offset, sort:newest price_min, price_max, beds_min, beds_max, baths_min, baths_max, property_type, property_type_nyc_only, new_construction, hide_pending_contingent, has_virtual_tours, has_3d_tours, hide_foreclosure, price_reduced, open_house, keywords, no_hoa_fee, hoa_max, days_on_realtor, expand_search_radius, include_nearby_areas_slug_id, home_size_min, home_size_max, lot_size_min, lot_size_max, home_age_max, stories, garage, heating_cooling, inside_rooms, outside_features, lot_views, community_ammenities, features_in_nyc_only`

optional_parameters.name: hide_foreclosure
optional_parameters.description: `true` for hide foreclosure. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: open_house
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with open house only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: expand_search_radius
optional_parameters.description: One of the following options: `1|5|10|25|50`. Expand search by radius in miles

optional_parameters.name: no_hoa_fee
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties without HOA fee only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: keywords
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. Get popular keywords from `/keywords-search-suggest` response

optional_parameters.name: price_reduced
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with price reduced only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: features_in_nyc_only
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `furniture|dishwasher|community_doorman|pets_allowed|laundry_room|elevator|community_outdoor_space`

optional_parameters.name: inside_rooms
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more comma separated from following options: `basement|hardwood_floors|fireplace|disability_features|den_or_office|family_room|dining_room`

optional_parameters.name: heating_cooling
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `central_air|central_heat|forced_air`

optional_parameters.name: property_type_nyc_only
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `condo|coop|condop`. For NYC listings only

optional_parameters.name: has_3d_tours
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with 3D tour only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: outside_features
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `swimming_pool|spa_or_hot_tub|horse_facilities`

optional_parameters.name: lot_views
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `waterfront|cul_de_sac|corner_lot|golf_course_lot_or_frontage|hill_or_mountain_view|ocean_view|lake_view|river_view`

optional_parameters.name: hide_pending_contingent

optional_parameters.name: limit
optional_parameters.description: Number of results. Maximum 200 for Paid Plan, default 42

optional_parameters.name: property_type
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `multi_family|single_family|mobile|land|farm`

optional_parameters.name: new_construction
optional_parameters.description: `true` for New construction only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: include_nearby_areas_slug_id
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. Expand search by including nearby areas. Get slug_id from `/location/for-sale-nearby-areas`

optional_parameters.name: sort
optional_parameters.description: One of the following options: `relevant|newest|lowest_price|highest_price|open_house_date|price_reduced_date|largest_sqft|lot_size|sold_date`. Default is relevant

optional_parameters.name: has_virtual_tours
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with virtual tour only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `community_swimming_pool|community_spa_or_hot_tub|community_golf|community_security_features|community_boat_facilities|tennis_court|community_clubhouse|senior_community`

data.profile_description: default agent role for MICHAEL DUKHOVNY
data.bio:
Ever since he was a child, Michael Dukhovny has always had the spirit and drive of a leader. His schooling and prior job and entrepreneurial experiences helped instill in him the mindset of a highly successful businessman. Upon first getting his real estate license, Michael briefly worked at Coldwell Banker and Infinity Brokerage. Soon he broke away to open up his own high-profile real estate company in Staten Island: ReMax United. After many successful years with the franchise, Michael wanted to broaden his horizons and real estate endeavors so he started United National Realty, a company specializing in residential real estate, commercial real estate, business sales, and corporate leasing all throughout the five boroughs of New York City and the Poconos (and still growing!). 
After more than fifteen years of diligent work and more than six hundred million dollars worth of sales, Michael Dukhovny still remains true to the pillars upon which he founded United National Realty: honesty and professionalism. He serves on the Staten Island Board of Realtors and is an active member of his community. Michael believes in establishing a personal connection with each of his clients so that it can be built into a relationship for life. He understands that each transaction is as unique as the people involved. Fluent in both English and Russian, he is highly respected amongst his peers, associates, and clients.
